data.description: Welcome to this four-bedroom, two-bathroom home nestled in a cul de sac in West Lancaster. The spacious family room serves as the heart of the home, boasting a charming fireplace and expansive sliding glass doors that lead out to the backyard pool. Come by and call me home for the New Year!
